&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and oversee custom client portfolios in collaboration with the IG.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor performance, exposures, and positioning to ensure alignment with client objectives and firm standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in manager due diligence, investment reviews, and contribute to IG and Investment Committee discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
