&lt;li&gt;Support business development efforts, including diagnostic reviews and RFP responses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build comprehensive knowledge of client-directed managers and portfolio positioning to deliver a seamless advisory experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
